# - Unicode characters are inserted as UTF-8
# - Storage-Effects: 1x UID
PATCH {{service}}(/books)/attribute::attrA HTTP/1.0
Storage: {{storage_patch_attribute}}
Content-Type: text/plain

№ <123> äüö &&amp; "§-ß" '€'

> {%
